data.description: Look no further ~ this charming rambler is All You need! One level living, featuring 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms & a 2-car attached garage. You're welcomed into your spacious living room, which flows nicely to the kitchen & eating area. Sunny kitchen has two windows behind the sink, allowing light to flow though. An eat-up bar makes quick meals a breeze. Nice-sized primary bdrm has a BIG walk-in closet.  Your privately fenced yard will be awesome for running & playing ~ bring your furry friends! Patio off the side of the home is great for BBQ's & roller blading. SUPER LOCATION !! All town amenities nearby ~ parks,  easy freeway access, Golf, restaurants, schools, Cheney Stadium for fun baseball games & much more!.
